# Task 11 – Create Flow in Flow Designer

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task automates the borrow request approval process using ServiceNow Flow Designer.

## Flow Name

Borrow Request Approval Flow

## Flow Process

1. Borrow Request is created with Status = Requested.
2. Flow is triggered automatically.
3. Approval request is sent to the Librarian.
4. If approved:
   - Book status changes to Issued.
   - Borrow Request status changes to Approved.
   - Student receives an email notification.
5. If rejected:
   - Borrow Request status changes to Rejected.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- Flow Designer
- Update Record Action
- Ask for Approval
- Send Email Notification

## Status

Completed
